com.sun.voip.client.connector
Class CallStatus

java.lang.Object
  com.sun.voip.client.connector.CallStatus
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class CallStatus
extends Object
implements Serializable

Represents call status, as returned from the bridge. Call status comes to us as a string, something like: SIPDialer/1.0 100 INVITED CallId='8' ConferenceId='JonCon' CallInfo='22500' We split this into 5 fields: Originator: SIPDialer/1.0 Code: 100 CallId: 8 ConferenceId: JonCon CallInfo: 22500
